# Screen capture + pointer control for the Vision agent. scrot is the SILENT grabber preferred
# for seamless capture (no shutter, no flash); grim covers Wayland; gnome-screenshot is the
# flashy last resort. xdotool moves/clicks the pointer for click-by-sight (X11 session).
scrot
grim
gnome-screenshot
xdotool
